Requires comment type

# Note

- If comment type doesn't match, error occurs.
- The error is unsound execution error which cannot be alleviated

# Arguments

- a_comment_type: A comment type to require.

# Demo

```
% If comment type is none or any...
$comment(start)
===
error: Critical unsound execution error 
= Comment type, "Start" is required but it is not
Int: Rad panicked with unrecoverable error.
```

# Example

$fassert($comment(start))
